  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Event Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>We’re looking for an Event Assistant who can turn ideas into unforgettable vibes.</strong></p><p>If you love creating meaningful, memorable experiences — and making sure every detail lands just right — this role was made for you.</p><p>Join a creative, collaborative team that values fresh perspectives and gives you the space to learn, experiment, and grow. Perfect for students, fresh graduates, or anyone eager to sharpen their event-planning skills.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and execute workshops, social events, and networking sessions people genuinely enjoy</li><li>Coordinate logistics, timelines, vendors, and on-site operations to keep events running seamlessly</li><li>Pitch fresh concepts — then bring them to life with flair</li><li>Work closely with the social/media team to promote events and boost engagement</li></ul><p><strong>You’ll Be a Great Fit If You…</strong></p><ul><li>Are a student, fresh graduate, or recently ORD and ready to get hands-on</li><li>Are organised yet creative — you love your checklists, but you’ve got big ideas too</li><li>Enjoy working with people and thrive in a team environment</li><li>Take initiative and adapt quickly when plans shift</li><li>Want to build practical skills and expand your network</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></p><ul><li>Real, hands-on event planning experience you can proudly showcase in your portfolio or resume</li><li>Flexible scheduling that fits around school or personal commitments</li><li>A supportive team that values your ideas and helps you grow</li><li>A relaxed, creative environment that still gets things done</li><li>Food, fun, and future opportunities — with potential to convert into a full-time role</li></ul><p>This isn’t just a student job — it’s your first step into something bigger.<br />If you’re ready to learn fast, meet new people, and help craft unforgettable experiences, we’d love to hear from you.</p><p><strong>Apply now — let’s make something amazing together!</strong></p>",
